            . I live in Ely-court, Holborn, and am a watchman. On the night of the 8th of May, I was in <placeName id="t18330516-76-crimeloc395">Holborn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18330516-76-crimeloc395" type="placeName" value="Holborn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18330516-76-crimeloc395" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330516-76-off393 t18330516-76-crimeloc395"></join>, and saw the prisoner following the prosecutor; there were others with the prisoner - I saw the prisoner pick the prosecutor's pocket of his handkerchief; I took him, he dropped the handkerchief, and I took it and him to the watch-house.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. He stated that there was a person with me who ran away. Witness. There was a person with him, but the prisoner picked the pocket - I caught him with it in his hand.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330516-76-person718">
                  PHILIP 
                  HARDWICK
