                  </persName>
            . I live in Russell-square. I lost this handkerchief in Holborn on the night of the 8th of May - I was told I had lost it, and then missed it - I had used it during the afternoon.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The other person took it, and threw it down.</p>
